sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K146001
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: AOX1 ethanol sensitive promoter cloned into RFP vector BBa_J61002
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: The AOX1 promoter was PCR amplified from pPCK3.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part is to be constructed by cloning part BBa_I764001 into the RFP vector BBa_J61002. Vector and insert are to be each digested with EcoRI and SpeI and ligated together to create the new composite part.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Dave Westenberg
